description:
S1ULink: Table containing information about S1-U links in a 5G network.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the data record.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant cell identifier (appears to be the same as CellId).
- Id3:  Likely an internal identifier (always '1' in sample data).
- Id4:  Combination of local and remote endpoints (likely redundant with S1ULink.s1ULinkId).
- vsDataType: Type of data (always 'vsDataS1ULink' in sample data).
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format (always 'EricssonSpecificAttributes' in sample data).
- S1ULink.s1ULinkId: Unique identifier of the S1-U link.
- S1ULink.remoteEndPoint: IP address of the remote endpoint of the S1-U link.
- S1ULink.localEndPoint: IP address of the local endpoint of the S1-U link.
